Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.15,0:24:43.25,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}願今後也能與你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.40,0:24:48.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}長久相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.64,0:24:53.57,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}如今我才初次知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.84,0:24:57.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}戀愛如此辛酸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.27,0:24:59.17,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}讓人痛苦
